      <title>中国人民银行债券交易大招让市场争论如何</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/pboc-s-bond-trading-drumbeat-leaves-market-debating-the-how</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的猜测称，中国人民银行将通过买卖政府债券来扩充其政策工具箱，市场观察人士对此展开争论，即这一举措在实践中将如何发挥作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/pboc-s-bond-trading-drumbeat-leaves-market-debating-the-how</guid>
